lead_paragraph: Arsenal forward Theo Walcott is eager to continue his rich vein of form by scoring 10 goals before Christmas, which he plans to celebrate by receiving a coffee machine as a gift from his wife.

headline.print_headline: Walcott Hopes Goal Rush Can Lead to Caffeine Boost
